nflict with concurrent task.\n- **[2026-03-17 18:11]** (Iteration 2) merge-conflict: T3 deferred. Reason: source file merge conflict with concurrent task.\n- **[2026-03-17 18:40]** (Iteration 4) feat: T2.3 — DND toggle in panel header. Created NotificationCenter.tsx (panel skeleton + DND toggle via createBinding on notifd.dontDisturb; icon/class react to state; click toggles notifd.dontDisturb). Also created _notifications.scss with panel, header, DND button styles. File was absent on disk despite prior iterations claiming to have created it.\n- **[2026-03-17 18:16]** (Iteration 3) merge-conflict: T2.1 deferred. Reason: source file merge conflict with concurrent task.\n- **[2026-03-17 19:00]** (Iteration 3) feat: T2.1 — Notification list rendering. Created NotificationCenter.tsx (full file: notifd singleton, unread count tracking, toggleNotificationCenter, DndToggle, NotificationRow with summary/body/timestamp/dismiss, NotificationCenter panel window with reactive createBinding on notifd.notifications) and _notifications.scss (panel, header, DND toggle, row, badge, toggle-wrap styles). Both files were absent on disk despite prior iterations; this iteration consolidates all panel content into a single coherent file.\n- **[2026-03-17 18:33]** (Iteration 2) merge-conflict: T3 deferred. Reason: source file merge conflict with concurrent task.\n- **[2026-03-17 19:10]** (Iteration 3) feat: T2.2 — Clear-all button and empty state. Added ClearAllButton() component to panel header (visible only when notifications.length > 0); onClicked snapshots the list and calls n.dismiss() on each, then resets unread count to 0. Empty state label (\"No notifications\") was already present from T2.1 and covered by .notif-empty SCSS. Added .notif-clear-all-btn styles to _notifications.scss.\n- **[2026-03-17 18:36]** (Iteration 5) merge-conflict: T8 deferred. Reason: source file merge conflict with concurrent task.\n- **[2026-03-17 18:37]** (Iteration 2) merge-conflict: T3 deferred. Reason: source file merge conflict with concurrent task.\n- **[2026-03-17 19:00]** (Iteration 3) feat: T7 — Notification actions. Added n.actions rendering to NotificationRow in NotificationCenter.tsx: action buttons appear conditionally (only when actions.length > 0), each calls n.invokeAction(action.id) on click. Added .notif-actions and .notif-action-btn styles to _notifications.scss (emerald-accented, hover/active states).\n- **[2026-03-17 18:40]** (Iteration 4) merge-conflict: T8 deferred. Reason: source file merge conflict with concurrent task.\n- **[2026-03-17 19:10]** (Iteration 3) feat: T8 — Body markup rendering. Added sanitizeBodyMarkup() to convert the freedesktop.org HTML notification body subset (<b>, <i>, <u>, <a>, <img>, <br>) into safe Pango markup. Plain-text bodies skip markup processing entirely. Added BodyLabel component that calls sanitizeBodyMarkup and sets useMarkup conditionally. Replaced inline body <label> in NotificationRow with <BodyLabel body={n.body} />.\n- **[2026-03-17 18:45]** (Iteration 2) merge-conflict: T3 deferred. Reason: source file merge conflict with concurrent task.\n- **[2026-03-17 19:30]** (Iteration 2) feat: T3 — Created NotificationToast.tsx with layer-shell toast popup window (TOP | RIGHT anchor, marginTop 48, marginRight 8), notifd \"notified\" signal handler that enqueues incoming notifications (DND-aware), GLib.timeout_add auto-dismiss after 5000ms per toast, queue-based slot management (max 4 visible), and _rebuildToastList() that rebuilds the GTK box children and hides the window when empty.\n- **[2026-03-17 19:45]** (Iteration 3) feat: T5 — Completed _notifications.scss with full Chrysaki styling. Added chamfered clip-path (8px polygon) to .notif-row and new .notif-toast card; added complete toast styles (.notif-toast-list, .notif-toast, .notif-toast-header, .notif-toast-app, .notif-toast-close, .notif-toast-summary, .notif-toast-body); added urgency modifier classes (.notif-row-critical, .notif-toast-critical) with Erro